Take N (number of rows - only odd numbers allowed), print the following pattern (for N = 5).

      *
   *  *  *  
*  *  *  *  *  
   *  *  *
      *
Input Format
Constraints
0 < N < 10 (only odd numbers allowed)

Output Format
Sample Input
5
Sample Output
      *
    * * *
  * * * * *
    * * *
      *
Explanation
Each '*' is separated from other by a tab.
